{"tid":2277886,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「玻璃又碎」 炭治郎耳環讓小粉紅崩潰 《鬼滅之刃》中國版挨刀","createTime":"2020-11-08T21:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T02:58:45.000Z","uid":310867,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7464fe6b7f78da20a9eb17dcc3b291c373ad9652","tid":2277886,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T21:02:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3345952?fbclid=IwAR1wHlOQXcK6mQmXmGOcGGyW8QOJ_sKyZn-NCYDD10YxtOKHcXYfqSDf_2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3345952%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1wHlOQXcK6mQmXmGOcGGyW8QOJ_sKyZn-NCYDD10YxtOKHcXYfqSDf_2I&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq79eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=a50ef5d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3345952%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1wHlOQXcK6mQmXmGOcGGyW8QOJ_sKyZn-NCYDD10YxtOKHcXYfqSDf_2I&h=fb0713c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3345952?fbclid=IwAR1wHlOQXcK6mQmXmGOcGGyW8QOJ_sKyZn-NCYDD10YxtOKHcXYfqSDf_2I</a><br />\n<br />\n《鬼滅之刃》主角竈門炭治郎配戴的耳環，意外挑動中國網友們的敏感神經，他們從預告中發現，耳環圖案近似日本的「旭日旗」，是第二次世界大戰時大日本帝國主義的象徵，甚至有中國網友痛斥「這年頭的作者能不能少表達一點過分惡劣的立場。煩」，顯然對此感到相當不滿。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在中國上映的與播出的《鬼滅之刃》電影、影集中，主角竈門炭治郎配戴的耳環與台灣上映的原版不同，這個被認為類似「旭日旗」的圖案消失了，取而代之的是紅色的圈圈、三條橫線，與1個灰色半圓形，但是中國民間自行推出的山寨周邊商品，仍有原版耳環的圖樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jovB227.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjovB227.png&h=f9d08210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，禁埋佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a782449d7d1b80eb928583899a6bf20940c03f","tid":2277886,"uid":310867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T21:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uKGuK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2